gle下 唔難搵<br />\n<br />\n自己小心蛋白質吸收過多 好傷肝（你唔做重訓既話）</blockquote><br />\n香港地食野，脂肪over哂蛋白質都未必夠標準<br />\n除非真係食好多肉"},{"pid":"ae62ef1177ceff9f5f0f4da493da3198f9d3aba5","tid":164831,"uid":37760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:05:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d39b2abd83ca08a77c4c570f4f131d09bbe661b","tid":164831,"uid":37760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:06:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dcab3d8509c6be573018abc7783fbac784b1cda","tid":164831,"uid":37760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"872621f8a5004f617e9f499879108f1e917da94b","tid":164831,"uid":79727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"Me 188cm 但得68Kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560158a0a6b27cba5d67adba454b6e240acd27cb","tid":164831,"uid":23496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:11:20.000Z","msg":"想增胖一定要靠做運動<br />\n<br />\n以前我又係成日嘈食極都唔增唔到重<br />\n<br />\n但係一兩前前開始勤做運動，再加埋好似以前食咁多嘢，就增磅增得好快 (46kg --&gt; 63kg)"},{"pid":"9796306887fcbca664077099585cb55ca1f78ead","tid":164831,"uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"碳水化合物，脂肪，糖<br />\n係得呢三樣野姐<br />\n每朝麵包，火腿煙肉腸，多士<br />\n午餐麵，飯，重口味野，得閒叫tea，奶茶多士，晚餐2碗飯，多肉。<br />\n<br />\n一個月，起碼肥2kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19693a8657810e4e29d73be0a28ff2c3ae9b648","tid":164831,"uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>碳水化合物，脂肪，糖<br />\n係得呢三樣野姐<br />\n每朝麵包，火腿煙肉腸，多士<br />\n午餐麵，飯，重口味野，得閒叫tea，奶茶多士，晚餐2碗飯，多肉。<br />\n<br />\n一個月，起碼肥2kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces